OL,3,CMan threatened to kill neighbour due
OL,4,Cto her dogs barking
OL,6,FA man who attacked his neighbour and
OL,7,Fthreatened to kill her because of her
OL,8,Fdogs barking has been jailed.
OL,10,FLiverpool Crown Court heard Anthony
OL,11,FLane, 38, threatened to kill both the
OL,12,Fwoman and her dogs before punching her
OL,13,Fand throwing her to the ground.
OL,15,FThe incident occurred at 9:40pm on 5
OL,16,FSeptember 2024 when Lane was visiting
OL,17,Fhis mum's house in Sefton.
