OL,3,CMan threatened to kill neighbour due
OL,4,Cto her dogs barking
OL,6,FThe victim, next-door neighbour
OL,7,FVivienne Davies, reported hearing a
OL,8,Fbanging noise before she heard Lane
OL,9,Fshout: "Shut those dogs up, I'll kill
OL,10,Fthem, and I'll kill you. My ma and da
OL,11,Fare trying to sleep."
OL,13,FMs Davies went to her back window and
OL,14,Fasked what was going on, to which Lane
OL,15,Fresponded with "garbled swearing".
OL,17,FProsecutor Sarah Egan said: "She
OL,18,Fgrabbed her phone and walked out the
OL,19,Ffront door, thinking this could be
OL,20,Fsorted out swiftly.
