OL,3,CMan threatened to kill neighbour due
OL,4,Cto her dogs barking
OL,6,F"The defendant walked to her property
OL,7,Fand was instantly aggressive. He was
OL,8,Fswearing about the dogs, saying he
OL,9,Fwould beat up the complainant's son.
OL,11,F"The complainant states that he picked
OL,12,Fup a spade from the garden and
OL,13,Fapproached her, holding it above his
OL,14,Fhead, as if to hit her. He threw the
OL,15,Fspade to the floor. The CCTV capturing
OL,16,Fthis is unclear."
OL,18,FLane, of Bank Road, Bootle, punched
OL,19,FMrs Davies on the arm insulted her
OL,20,Fsaid he would knock her out and her
OL,21,Fson.
